headline: GTA Online
subtitle: On the Podium This Week: Överflöd Tyrant
content: If you find yourself visiting The Diamond Casino & Resort this week, make sure to show the Lucky Wheel some love by giving it a spin. Who knows, you could walk away with GTA$, RP, clothing, plus all sorts of mystery prizes. This week the Överflöd Tyrant, a veritable Category Four storm on wheels, is on the podium.
